Spyder AsyncAPI Parser (1.0.alpha-SNAPSHOT 2021/03/14 15-29-33)

An open source java based AsyncAPI 2.0 document parser.

Please note that this is not a validator; it will attempt to parse any well formed AsyncAPI-like source.

To get started, see the code sample at AsyncAPIParserFactory.

Richer documentation can be found here

Please contribute on github
